TI  - Remote sensing of selective logging in Amazonia - Assessing limitations based on detailed field observations, Landsat ETM+, and textural analysis
T2  - REMOTE SENSING OF ENVIRONMENT
KW  - RAIN-FOREST
KW  - MANAGEMENT
KW  - IMPACTS
