TI  - Poverty and environment in Amazonia: A specific challenge for joint implementation
T2  - GREENHOUSE GAS MITIGATION: TECHNOLOGIES FOR ACTIVITIES IMPLEMENTED JOINTLY
KW  - tropical forests
KW  - recuperation of degraded areas
KW  - natural materials for industry
