TI  - Plant succession, landscape management, and the ecology of frugivorous birds in abandoned Amazonian pastures
T2  - CONSERVATION BIOLOGY
KW  - OLD FIELD VEGETATION
KW  - FOREST
KW  - DISPERSAL
